# System Log

> **Owner:** All agents (Zimmer primary, others append)
> **Format:** Reverse-chronological. Most recent entry at the top.
> **Gitignored:** `state/system-log.md` is never committed. This template is.

---

## How to Write an Entry

```
### [YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM] — [Stage N] [Event summary]
**Agent:** [Zimmer / Tanmay / Leonardo / Mark / Human]
- [What happened]
- [What was produced / decided]
- [Next action and owner]
```

